PreRequisites: FACTS Activity Polygons feature class updated with a linked SUID to the FACT_ACTV160_VW view. It is higly advisable to select as few FACTS polygons as possible before you run this vis. It takes a LONG time to return an answer, and even longer the more polygons you have selected. Results: A new feature class is added to your output path and added to your ArcMap table of contents.
The SQL that runs to return this data can be easily viewed after it is run. If you would like help with this, please put in a CHD ticket.
